@startuml
title Secuencia - Solicitud, evaluacion y desembolso BanBif

skinparam shadowing false

actor "Cliente BanBif" as Cliente
participant "Homebanking" as Home
participant "API Homebanking" as ApiHome
database "bd_core_financiero" as DB
participant "API Core Financiero" as ApiCore
actor "Analista" as Analista
actor "Agencia" as Agencia

== Solicitud del cliente ==

Cliente -> Home: Ingresa con DNI y clave
Home -> ApiHome: Login cliente
ApiHome -> DB: Validar credenciales
DB --> ApiHome: Cliente valido
ApiHome --> Home: Token cliente

Cliente -> Home: Solicita Prestamo Efectivo BanBif
Home -> ApiHome: Enviar monto, plazo e ingreso
ApiHome -> ApiHome: Calcular cuota y RDS
ApiHome -> ApiHome: Asignar score, riesgo y ruta
ApiHome -> DB: INSERT creditapplication
DB --> ApiHome: Solicitud registrada
ApiHome --> Home: Estado En evaluacion

== Evaluacion interna ==

Analista -> ApiCore: Consultar bandeja
ApiCore -> DB: SELECT solicitudes segun rol
DB --> ApiCore: Solicitudes asignadas
ApiCore --> Analista: Bandeja de creditos

Analista -> ApiCore: Abrir detalle tecnico
ApiCore -> DB: SELECT cliente, cuenta y credito
DB --> ApiCore: Datos completos
ApiCore --> Analista: TEA, TCEA, seguro, cuota, RDS, score y riesgo

Analista -> ApiCore: Aprobar, rechazar o derivar
ApiCore -> ApiCore: Validar JWT, rol y autonomia
ApiCore -> DB: UPDATE creditapplication
DB --> ApiCore: Decision registrada

== Desembolso ==

Agencia -> ApiCore: Desembolsar credito aprobado
ApiCore -> ApiCore: Validar rol Agencia
ApiCore -> DB: INSERT credit_disbursement
ApiCore -> DB: INSERT movement
ApiCore -> DB: UPDATE account.balance
ApiCore -> DB: INSERT loan_schedule
DB --> ApiCore: Desembolso completado
ApiCore --> Agencia: Confirmacion

== Retorno al Homebanking ==

Cliente -> Home: Consulta cuenta
Home -> ApiHome: Obtener saldo y movimientos
ApiHome -> DB: SELECT account + movement
DB --> ApiHome: Saldo actualizado
ApiHome --> Home: Muestra desembolso

@enduml
